reviewText: No one like this singing cowboy and his horse. In a  (movie)world filled with excessive bloody violence, these Autry movies are a real pleasure to watch over and over again. Film quality is also very good!
Timely arrive for sure. It's a Christmas present. Love the embossed tin it came in and can't wait to view it!
This was a present to myself and I enjoyed watching all of the movies that were on the DVD's.  It brought back memories of the westerns of long ago.
Great for older generations.  It was a great gift.
Fantastic set. Really like the embossed tin.
Gave this as a gift to an elderly gentleman who enjoys older westerns, and he really enjoyed it!
